    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Le programme est ax&#xE9; sur le renforcement des capacit&#xE9;s institutionnelles n&#xE9;cessaires au d&#xE9;veloppement durable des 37 pays b&#xE9;n&#xE9;ficiaires. Il permet de plus de renforcer partenariats institutionnels entre les pays membres de la Francophonie, l&#x2019;internationalisation et la promotion &#xE0; l&#x2019;&#xE9;tranger de l&#x2019;&#xE9;ducation et de la formation canadienne. Enfin, le PCBF permet de d&#xE9;velopper les capacit&#xE9;s des institutions des communaut&#xE9;s francophones en situation minoritaire (Alberta, Manitoba, Nouveau Brunswick, Nouvelle-&#xC9;cosse et Ontario) en int&#xE9;grant les boursiers aux programmes de formation en fran&#xE7;ais dans ces r&#xE9;gions.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program focuses on building the institutional capacities needed for sustainable development in the 37 recipient countries. It also helps strengthen institutional partnerships between Francophonie member countries, as well as the globalization and the international promotion of Canadian education and training. Lastly, the CFSP helps to build the capacities of institutions in Francophone minority communities (Alberta, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia and Ontario) by integrating the scholars into French-language training programs in these regions.</narrative>
    </description>
